DATA_DIR=data
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434/api/generate
OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1
OLLAMA_TIMEOUT=90
OLLAMA_STREAM=true
OLLAMA_NUM_PREDICT=600
OLLAMA_NUM_CTX=4096
PROMPT_MAX_LINES_PER_DOC=60
PROMPT_MAX_CHARS=4500
MAX_RETRIES=2
MAX_FILE_SIZE=1000000
EXTRACTION_RULES=Be strict and evidence-based. Return JSON only. Normalize geography when unambiguous from visible city, region, postal code, phone/calling code, or country code. country_code must be ISO alpha-2, not a phone code. Apply geography/nationality inference globally: fill nationality from a confident country/place/address signal when blank and not conflicting. Never place country/city/region/postal data or nested objects in street.
